about.description1: We are a platform offering comprehensive housing solutions. Whatever your residential needs, 88go will be your reliable partner. We look forward to providing you with the best quality service on this housing journey and working with you to realize a new future in living.
about.description2: 88go brings together numerous high-quality listings, covering various needs and budgets. From cozy apartments to spacious villas, from downtown cores to serene suburbs, our listings are diverse and are sure to meet your requirements. We also provide multiple devices for browsing, allowing you to find your ideal home anytime, anywhere.
about.slogan4: No Agent Fees, Save Your Expenses
about.description3: We believe renting or buying a house should be easy and enjoyable, not burdened by hefty costs. 88go promises not to let complicated agent fees be a barrier to your housing choice. With just a small membership fee, you can enjoy secure real estate transactions and maximize your benefits from the deals.
about.slogan5: Worry-Free Renting, Partners Taking Care of You!
about.description4: At 88go, we are dedicated to creating a secure and smooth transaction experience for you, enabling you to confidently choose your ideal residence. Our partnered professionals, with their rich experience and expertise, assist you at every step of the housing transaction. Whether it's legal support, transaction protection, or handling details, they go the extra mile to ensure your interests are maximally protected.
about.slogan6: Let us make the deal on your home
about.getStared: Get started today and find the right person and your home!
about.description5: At 88go, we provide you with a platform to start searching for your ideal home as well as good housing offers. Whether you are a tenant or a landlord, we will help you find the right home and the right deal. Let's start this exciting journey together!

agent.slogan1: Three-Generation Profit, Creating Residential Income Together!
agent.subSlogan: Invite others to join; successful transactions will bring you benefits.
agent.description1: In order to ensure that every member enjoys more returns, 88go has specially introduced our unique three-generation profit-sharing program. When you successfully invite others to join as members, you will also receive a share of their transaction profits. What's even more exciting is that you can also share the agent's profit from their referrals, not limited to your transactions, but also including the members you referred and those they referred.
agent.joinDescription2: Before joining 88go, you can become part of someone else's agents by entering their code. Once you become our member, you also have the opportunity to become an agent.
agent.becomeMemberDescription: After becoming a member, you will receive a unique agent code. You can share this code with friends and family around you, inviting them to join 88go.
agent.becomeAgentDescription: Once you successfully invite others to join, you will have the status of an agent. Through the agent program, you will receive commission income, and you can also share the transaction profits of the people you referred.
agent.inviteDescription: The chain effect allows your influence and earnings to continuously expand. The more people you invite, the more commission you will receive.
agent.accountingDescription: Income statistics from the 1st to the 30th of each month will be remitted in the following month. Members can also view performance rewards in real-time, ensuring that your rewards are timely and transparent.
agent.profitsDescription: 1 per month - Even if the members you refer refer, you can share in their trading interests.
agent.joinHands: Join Hands to Share the Glory of Living!
agent.joinHandsDescription: This chain effect allows your influence and earnings to continue to expand, making you an important part of a community that wins together in living. 88go believes that this mutually beneficial model can bring more value to each member and together we can create a better future for renting and buying.

policy.description1: Welcome to 88go Property Trading Platform (hereinafter referred to as "we" or "the platform"). Please read the following membership rules carefully before using our services. Registering as our member signifies your agreement to comply with these rules and statements.
policy.description2: We highly value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. Our Privacy Policy outlines in detail how we collect, use, and protect your information.

list.description4: 2.2 If we find that you are an agent, your account will be immediately deleted, and the plan you originally purchased will not be refunded.

list.description8: 4.2 You are not allowed to publish false information, content that infringes on the rights of others, or engage in illegal activities on the platform.

mortgageCalculator.paymentInEqual: Payment in equal installments, interest calculated on decreasing balance
mortgageCalculator.para1: The loan calculation function is a function provided by Vietnam Commercial Bank to assist customers in estimating the interest and principal amount required to pay for a loan.
mortgageCalculator.para2: To use the loan calculation feature, customers need to provide some basic information about their loan, including:
mortgageCalculator.para3: Based on this information, the function will calculate and display the following information to the customer:
mortgageCalculator.list3: Total amount to be paid for the entire loan
mortgageCalculator.para4: The Vietnam Bank Loan Calculator function is a useful tool that helps customers estimate the cost of a loan before deciding to borrow. This feature also helps customers compare interest rates and loan terms between banks to choose the loan that best suits their needs.
mortgageCalculator.para5: How to use Vietnam Bank loan calculation function
mortgageCalculator.para6: To use the Vietnam Bank loan calculation function, customers can follow the steps below:
mortgageCalculator.list4: Visit the website or mobile banking app of the bank where you want to borrow money.
mortgageCalculator.list5: Look for the loan calculator feature.
mortgageCalculator.list6: Enter the necessary information about your loan.
mortgageCalculator.list8: Loan amount: The amount of money you want to borrow from the bank.
mortgageCalculator.list9: Loan interest rate: The interest rate you will pay for a loan. Loan rates are usually calculated annually, but you can enter a monthly loan rate if the feature allows.
mortgageCalculator.list10: Loan term: How long you have to repay the loan. Loan terms are usually calculated in years, but if the feature allows, you can enter the loan term in months.
mortgageCalculator.list11: Monthly Principal Payment: The amount of principal you need to pay each month to gradually reduce your loan.
mortgageCalculator.list12: Monthly Interest Payment: The amount of interest you pay each month on your loan.
mortgageCalculator.list13: Total Loan Payment: The total amount of principal and interest you need to pay for the entire loan.
mortgageCalculator.list14: The information displayed by the Vietnam Bank loan calculation function is for reference only. Actual interest and principal amounts may vary based on other factors, such as inflation and market interest rates.
mortgageCalculator.list15: You should consult a banking expert for detailed advice on your loan.

forumPage.ruleDes: Please be sure to read the forum rules carefully before submitting articles. All members must abide by the above principles. If you disagree, please do not post comments here.
forumPage.ruleItem1: Members of the 88go Trading Network are free to comment on all articles. The topics and content on this forum do not represent the position of 88go. forumPage.ruleItem2: Before publishing an article, members must confirm that the content (pictures) of the article they post does not infringe the copyright, trademark, patent and other rights of others. If any legal liability arises from articles published by members, they will be borne by the members themselves.
forumPage.ruleItem3: Members agree not to post anything in the forum that is fraudulent, defamatory, false, abusive, vulgar, harmful, harassing, obscene, profane, sexually oriented, threatens to invade another person's privacy, or violates any Information on legal regulations. If found to be reported, 88go has the right to delete it on its own. If the circumstances are serious, the member's qualifications will be revoked.
